race.description: Rmbl Investments Rising Stars Race Handicap
race.comment: Good race for the rising stars in the saddle. MASKED MARAUDER (3) was a fresh-up winner then midfield last time in heavy ground at Bendigo. Better than that and will sit handy in the run. Worth another chance. SHAALUTE (1) raced on speed last time and wasn't far away in tougher company at Sandown Hillside. Has a low draw and will give a sight again. AYSGARTH (2) is fitter for two runs back and ran a much better race last time. Fitter again and did place last time in when third-up. Looks a major player. HEADSTOCK (7) boxed on well fresh after sitting handy in the run and strips fitter. Tricky gate but rates well here on best figures. AFFIRMATIVE LAD (5) has been racing well. Nicely drawn and will wind up strongly.
